ygData.subject: Re: Types of dungeons?
ygData.msgSnippet: EQ lizer (http://gameznet.com/eq) has maps of some of the zones (dungeons are considered zones).  It also has alot of other nice information I have found
ygData.messageBody:
EQ'lizer (http://gameznet.com/eq) has maps of some of the zones (dungeons
are considered zones). It also has alot of other nice information I have
found useful such as equipment locations, levels of mobs, what levels each
zone is targeted at, etc.

> From: "ken satchell \"flash-net & nikken distrubter\"" <ken4p@...>
